<plot>Chasing The Monochrome Rainbow is a film that focuses on clinical depression and the struggle to find a place to be able to cope with life again. It follows the feelings of a woman who must deal with her illness as she battles to function normally and keep her family together. The piece touches on the stigma associated with the condition revealing that in the end there are no easy answers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100817</url></doc>
